-- BP May Increase Disposal of Assets to as Much as $15 Billion, Times Says
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-07-09T02:31:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/bp-may-increase-disposal-of-assets-to-as-much-as-15-billion-times-says.html

          
          
             BP Plc  is considering increasing its
asset disposal program to as much as $15 billion from $10
billion, the London-based  Times reported , without saying how it
obtained the information.  
 “If opportunities come up to dispose of other parts of the
business then those will be considered,” the newspaper reported
an unnamed spokeswoman for the company as saying.  
 BP’s board will meet in two weeks to consider the future
direction of the company, the  newspaper also said .  
